data.description: This classic Traditional style Ranch is a  3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a lot to offer its next owners, with a private room toward the back that can be used a multiple ways as an additional sleeping area or an office or studio!  Freshly painted both inside and out and has a new roof as of 02/2023 and HVAC as of 06/2020.This spacious home even has new tile work in the shower of the main bathroom. So you want more? This home also features a very cute and comfortable Studio attached Apartment  to use for guest as in Friends and or Family or use as an office or private space.    The yard is spacious in the offering with being a corner lot with anadditional shed for storage. Within Minutes of Charming Downtown Plant City with its cafes, Famous Antique Shoppes, Lovely parks and Restaurants. Gilchrist Park and the Dog Park  is a short Distance away. Within a couple of miles you can be close to I-4 and to all Plant City has to offer. Good News! This Home qualifies for the Hillsborough County First Time Home Buyers Program With Up to $25000 help in funds for Down Payment and closing cost.  Act Now don't let this opportunity to be a Home Owner pass you by.  Come take a look.
